{"tid":1803796,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(全球黃色經濟圈) 玻宗教司:全球穆斯林抵制中國貨 把穆產品推到全世界","createTime":"2019-12-30T13:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T18:42:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3b849bb2a20f5dd446816bbe64c5dffe8a5356b3","tid":1803796,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"玻璃市宗教司拿督斯里阿斯林今日呼籲全球穆斯林罷買中國商品，以此向中國施壓，關閉新疆維吾爾族的「職業技能教育培訓中心」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他在2019年吉隆坡峰會期間接受《半島電視台》訪問時，呼籲穆斯林世界的政治與宗教領袖通過經濟和外交手段，向中國施壓，讓中方停止侵害新疆維族的權益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我們甚至需要抵制中國產品，他們（中國）知道我們的購買力。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿斯林也在峰會上表示，全球逾20億穆斯林人口應該展示經濟能力，以影響世界各國的政策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://c4news.site/archives/61292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc4news.site%2Farchives%2F61292&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=bc166717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://c4news.site/archives/61292</a>"},{"pid":"f7376fb9a93848bc5dab2b9a862d5c8e5f75fc85","tid":1803796,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:05:15.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=025191d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=59a7c198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要32000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=2cd755b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">簽完share條link去tg</span></span>"},{"pid":"b656e62e5201c75bcc4f04669855a1dd9b39162a","tid":1803796,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:05:26.000Z","msg":"#boycottmadeinchina"},{"pid":"dc770fcb0ca048740e071b02ad859d62a5dea1a1","tid":1803796,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OH8CmKO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOH8CmKO.jpg&h=70f14856&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce5c3a825d2bcc3f2f2157ee27e8e36c29c7d4ec","tid":1803796,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:06:35.000Z","msg":"「我們應該做些東西，因為他們（維吾爾族）是我們的兄弟姐妹。」<br />\n<br />\n因此，他建議，「優先購買穆斯林」運動應該推動到全世界，以團結穆斯林國家的購買力，從而捍衛穆斯林的權益。<br />\n<br />\n他也認為，「優先購買穆斯林」運動在國內推動失敗的原因，主要摻雜了宗教及種族的因素在內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據西方媒體報道，中國政府打壓新疆維吾爾族，並建立集中營來管理；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，中國政府駁斥此說法，並強調有關營地是「職業技能教育培訓中心」，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n設立的目的是要打擊恐怖主義活動，以及消除極端思想的志願寄宿學校。<br />\n<br />\n他也認為，購買由伊斯蘭國家出產的商品是穆斯林的責任。<br />\n<br />\n根據《自由今日大馬》報導，阿斯里今日出席吉隆坡峰會，一場名為「重新分配財富：共享繁榮」講座會時說，全球約17億穆斯林能提高穆斯林國家的購買力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n「這等購買力能幫助伊斯蘭國家。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他也提及我國的「先購買穆斯林產品」運動，指當一名穆斯林呼籲其他穆斯林購買這類商品，就被標籤為種族主義。<br />\n<br />\n「我們又沒叫人杯葛非穆斯林商品。」<br />\n<br />\n他還說，這項運動純粹幫助大馬穆斯林繁榮。<br />\n<br />\n他說，穆斯林在商界表現頗弱，特別是馬來西亞和印尼的穆斯林。<br />\n<br />\n「他們面對推銷穆斯林產品的問題。」<br />\n<br />\n他也說，許多伊斯蘭國家仍依賴西方國家，儘管擁有石油與天然氣的豐富資源，但仍成為「傀儡」。<br />\n<br />\n他說，這導致伊斯蘭國家欠缺能團結所有穆斯林的貿易群體。<br />\n<br />\n「這對穆斯林而言是一種悲慘的現實。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因此，他呼籲所有穆斯林鞏固「伊斯蘭團結」，從而達到經濟自由。<br />\n<br />\n他說，此舉也有助於解決非清真食品的問題，同時保障食品安全。"},{"pid":"43c1b9a13988779b11a6425c6171f2b859754da2","tid":1803796,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"你地叫到什葉派班陷家鏟唔好同支那軍演未？"},{"pid":"c230108eab063d02b9770c9cc12cdd35eb3cfaf3","tid":1803796,"uid":170335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:26:57.000Z","msg":"反共經濟圈"},{"pid":"770ec751be6dd5c99bd299483886b028ecbea5ee","tid":1803796,"uid":48318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[極限挑戰] <span style=\"color: red;\">德國第三份聯署，最後48小時</span>，要多3萬人，連登仔做唔做到?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803447\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803447</a><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=2cd755b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3067cda055c67032d066b3c12441518e647b990f","tid":1803796,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43c1b9a13988779b11a6425c6171f2b859754da2","tid":1803796,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"你地叫到什葉派班陷家鏟唔好同支那軍演未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T13:29:53.000Z","msg":"一步步嚟，依家起碼叫有個好開始先"},{"pid":"7efed0d161ba10e3284e64358ef40143837b5ae7","tid":1803796,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc